These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, iris, rose, aconite
1. the person who growsaconite is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3
2. the person who growstulip is somewhere to the right of the person who growsaconite##5
3. the person who growsiris is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
4. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1       |     2      |   3   |   4    |
| Flower   | rose | iris | aconite | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: aquamarine, lilac, apricot, grey
1. the person who likes aquamarine is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
2. the person who likes lilac is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes apricot##2
3. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
4. the person who likes grey is somewhere to the right of the person who likes aquamarine##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |  2   |    3     |    4    |
| Color   | aquamarine | apricot | lilac | grey |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-3::.
