.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-8-4::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, goat, mouse, rabbit
1. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the goat##7
2. the owner of the rabbit is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
3. the owner of the mouse is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the mouse is not to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |      2      |       3       |   4    |
| Pet   | goat | rabbit | mouse | hedgehog |

