2. the person who's birthday is in september is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##5
4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who's birthday is in february##7
5. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in march##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | march | may | september | february |

